.IX Header "SHExpandDH"
.IP "SHExpandDH \-" 13
.IX Item "SHExpandDH -"
Expand an equally sampled or equally spaced grid into spherical harmonics using Driscoll and Healy's (1994) sampling theorem.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.IP "\s-1SUBROUTINE\s0 SHExpandDH (" 24
